::Shadow Wing::

She saw them take off into the woods.  She opened her wings and flew 
after them.  She stayed behind them and over to the side a little to 
avoid detection.  She hoped from this height, that even if they saw 
her, she would be mistaken for a real owl passing by.
Off in the distance, she thought she heard a jet again.  She shook 
her head. Must be my audio sensors playing with me, she thought.
